## 🔄 Data Flow Verification

### Upload Flow ✅
```
Browser → POST /files/upload (multipart/form-data)
  → FileController.uploadFiles()
  → UserService.findByUsername() [DB query: users table]
  → FileStorageService.uploadFile()
    → FileRepository.sumFileSizeByUser() [quota check]
    → UUID filename generation
    → StorageNodeService.selectNode() [random node1/2/3]
    → Files.copy() [disk write: storage/nodeX/uuid.ext]
    → SHA-256 hash computation
    → FileRepository.findFirstByFileHash() [dedup check]
    → FileRepository.save() [DB insert: files table]
  → redirect:/files
```

### Share Flow ✅
```
POST /share/generate/{fileId}
  → FileStorageService.getFileEntity() [ownership check]
  → SharedLinkService.generateShareLink() → SharedLinkRepository.save()
  → redirect:/files (flash: shareLink token)

GET /share/{token} [PUBLIC - no login]
  → SharedLinkService.resolveShareLink() [find by token, check expiry]
  → file.isDeleted() check
  → renders shared.html with file metadata

GET /share/download/{token} [PUBLIC]
  → Same checks + Files.exists() physical check
  → Returns UrlResource as octet-stream
```

### Admin Role Toggle ✅
```
POST /admin/users/toggle-role/{id}
  → AdminController [ROLE_ADMIN required by SecurityConfig]
  → self-demotion check
  → userRepository.save() [updates role field]
```

